               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390408-name-108" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-108" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-108" type="surname" value="PEARCE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-108" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES PEARCE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in James-street, East India-road. On the after<lb></lb>noon of the 19th of March I was in Aldersgate-street—there were two young men behind—I felt one touch me—I turned, and saw the prisoner cross the road from behind me—I told Mr. Rose, who was with me, I had lost my handkerchief—he followed the prisoner, and soon after produced the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
