                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-109" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE ROSE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Little Burton-street. I was with Mr. Pearce, and followed the prisoner, who ran across the road—he took the handkerchief from under the breast of his coat, and threw it under the horse of a brew<lb></lb>er's dray—I took it up, pursued him, and gave him into custody.</p>
